overview: Her talents go from acting, to fashion, dancing and singing. With a net worth over 250 million dollars, J.Lo has conquered the Latin American and pop music scene.  From the streets of the Bronx to the red carpets of Hollywood, she has achieved more than most would dream for.  Follow the story of one of the most talented and successful women in showbiz. The real Latina diva, Jennifer Lopez.
tagline: Follow the story of one of the most talented and successful women in Hollywood showbiz. The real Latina diva, Jennifer Lopez.
title: J. Lo: Let's Get Real
